Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.60,0:01:30.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I hope to see you tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.53,0:01:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when we have this session
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you can ask us anything you want
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.10,0:01:41.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we are all living through phenomenal digital revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.73,0:01:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,advances in technology and data acquisition
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.33,0:01:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and artificial intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.17,0:01:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,have impacted just about every corner of our live
