Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.20,0:01:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but around the globe to some 7 billion people
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and many of these things are wonderful
