Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:59.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about democratization
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.33,0:02:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of access to information and technology
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.00,0:02:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and bring the world closer
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.17,0:02:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and communication
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,on betas with every innovation there are dark sides
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:09.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and as a young
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.77,0:02:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,budding computer scientist we shouldn't ignore those
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.90,0:02:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we should pay attention to the ethical issues
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the potential harm
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.53,0:02:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that can come
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.40,0:02:23.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from technologies that we ourselves are developing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.17,0:02:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and that's what this lecture is about today
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by way of a case study
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.87,0:02:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to be talking a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.33,0:02:31.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about ethical issues around artificial intelligence
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:34.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and data and the work I'm going to be describing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.57,0:02:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is that of julia dressa
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.87,0:02:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,julia was a student with me at dartmouth college
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.37,0:02:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she graduated in 2007
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the work I'm going to be describing was
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,her senior thesis work
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.17,0:02:48.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and this work all started
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.67,0:02:52.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,around this issue of the use of ai
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.17,0:02:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to make recommendations
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.90,0:02:56.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now you have all
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.47,0:02:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,almost certainly been subjected to a recommendation
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.20,0:03:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that looks something like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.10,0:03:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you liked x then you may like y
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.20,0:03:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Netflix amazon spotify
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.13,0:03:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,recommendations that look
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at the patterns of movies you watch
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.07,0:03:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,products you buy music that you listen to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.00,0:03:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,look at what other people have done with those
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.00,0:03:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,same patterns and make recommendations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.33,0:03:20.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,sometimes it works sometimes it doesn't
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:21.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,either way it's fine
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.97,0:03:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean there's just recommendations for watching movies
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.47,0:03:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now you may have also been subjected
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.37,0:03:30.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a recommendation engine that looks something like this
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you are like x then we may accept you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.10,0:03:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,companies in some cases universities
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are using automatic algorithms
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.07,0:03:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to review your applications and make determinations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:45.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,as to whether you should be interviewed
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.13,0:03:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or granted a job
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,your the stakes are of course
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.73,0:03:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,getting a little bit higher now
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.93,0:03:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because we are talking about your potential employment
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.47,0:03:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and educational prospects
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,maybe you have not already because you're all young
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.20,0:03:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but many of us have been subjected to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.37,0:04:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,predictions that look like this
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.73,0:04:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you are like acts then we may give you alone
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.40,0:04:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,banks financial institutions routinely look
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.33,0:04:09.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at your credit history
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.13,0:04:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,your history in financial transactions
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,compares that to other people
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:18.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,looks to see what the default rates are
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.10,0:04:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and make recommendations
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.30,0:04:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do you get a mortgage do you get a small business loan
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.27,0:04:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,stakes are giving a little bit higher now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.97,0:04:27.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is now your financial well being as well
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and more and more over the last few years
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.30,0:04:32.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,people have been subjected
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.57,0:04:34.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to the following type of prediction
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you are like axe
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.67,0:04:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then we may put you in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,courts now around the country are routinely using
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.57,0:04:45.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,predictive algorithms to determine whether you are at
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.47,0:04:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,risk of committing a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,whether you are being released on probation
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.20,0:04:52.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,whether you be unconsidered for bail
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:54.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now the stakes are getting very high
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.10,0:04:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is now it is your very liberty that is a stake
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.77,0:04:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for these prediction algorithms
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it is these types of algorithms in particular
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.07,0:05:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that we're going to talk about today
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now in 2006 pro publica wrote a really impactful piece
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:12.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and if you have not seen this
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to encourage you
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.00,0:05:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to search for this piece called machine bias
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they're softer
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,used across the country to predict future criminals
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.90,0:05:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it is biased against blacks
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it was a phenomenal body of reporting
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that pointed to some very troubling patterns
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.30,0:05:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in a softer that was being used in the courts of law
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.07,0:05:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to make predictions
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.47,0:05:36.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about whether somebody is at
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,risk of committing a crime in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.30,0:05:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and whether that person should be granted bail or not
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.87,0:05:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so let me talk a little bit
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.67,0:05:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about what this article found
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I'm going to tell you a little bit of that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.70,0:05:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about what julia and I
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,worked on for the following year to try to really
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.90,0:05:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,understand
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what's happening with this type of machine bias
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.93,0:05:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so a pro publica found is that one particular software
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.90,0:06:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,produced what's called the recidivism risk score
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.60,0:06:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this essential takes his input
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.57,0:06:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,some information about you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.47,0:06:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how many times you've been committed a crime before
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how many times you've been arrested
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.10,0:06:11.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how much time you served in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:13.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,your employment history
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.27,0:06:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,your age your gender
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the long list of things that you might
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.33,0:06:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,have information
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.33,0:06:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and it produced a score
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.53,0:06:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and that score was
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.13,0:06:23.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what is your risk of committing a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.00,0:06:25.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in the next two years
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then that could be used
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.10,0:06:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and in fact was being used by the courts
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.77,0:06:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to make a judge minus to whether you were at risk for
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.67,0:06:36.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,recivivating and whether they should grant you bell
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.50,0:06:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and what pro publica found
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.97,0:06:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,is that the mistakes that this
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.93,0:06:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,algorithm made it
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:41.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's okay
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.40,0:06:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we understand that these things are not perfect
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.60,0:06:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but the nature of the mistakes were very problematic
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.40,0:06:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to talk about two types of mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.30,0:06:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the first one is a false positive
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.97,0:06:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which says I'm going to predict that you recidivate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.33,0:06:55.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but you in fact don't
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.67,0:06:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'm going to classify you as high risk
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.50,0:07:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but in fact you are not high risk at all
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.27,0:07:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and what they found is that if you were black
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.27,0:07:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,then you were 44.9% of the times you were predicted
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.97,0:07:10.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to recidivate when you didn't
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if you were right that was only about half of that
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:14.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,23 and a half percent
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.67,0:07:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that is a huge difference
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.10,0:07:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,across the races
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so that is black people were being
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.67,0:07:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,falsely accused of being high risk
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:25.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one in fact they were not
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.70,0:07:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,at a rate twice that of white people
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.27,0:07:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now that's not the only type of mistakes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that the algorithm makes
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it also can make a false negative
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,which is that you are predicted not to recidivate
