Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I say you know what this person's not high risk
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.93,0:07:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but it turns out they go out and they commit a crime
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so let's look at the error rate for these
