Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.77,0:07:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,for across races
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.40,0:07:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you were black
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.37,0:07:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that error only happened 28% of the time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.30,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but if you were white it happened 47.7% of the time
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.90,0:07:57.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,exactly the opposite
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.77,0:07:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so in the previous false positive
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.10,0:08:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,blacks were at about a factor of two disadvantage
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of saying they were high risk when they weren't
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.77,0:08:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and not only that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.37,0:08:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but in this mistake's white are being advantaged
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,by saying that they are not high risk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.60,0:08:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when they are
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.47,0:08:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so obviously this is deeply troubling
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.30,0:08:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is not obviously fair
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.47,0:08:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we need to understand this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.53,0:08:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if we're going to use these types of ai algorithms
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:26.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we need to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.60,0:08:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,where is this coming from and what can we do about it
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.47,0:08:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so shortly after this article appear
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.87,0:08:32.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,julia came to me and said
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.27,0:08:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have to do something about this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.53,0:08:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we are technologists we are mathematicians
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.13,0:08:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we are computer scientists
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.50,0:08:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have to fix this
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.30,0:08:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have to build a better prediction algorithm
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.53,0:08:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I agreed with her
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.80,0:08:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we set out over the next year and a half or so
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.17,0:08:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to try to do that
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.97,0:08:48.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and as we were doing that a question came up
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.33,0:08:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we were sitting in my office one day
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.30,0:08:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.53,0:08:53.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,one of us asked the question as well
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.40,0:08:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you know we keep trying to come up with
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.10,0:08:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,algorithms that are better
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.93,0:08:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,than humans but
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do we actually know
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what how good humans are at this task
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.73,0:09:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean just baseline
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.20,0:09:04.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean if you're trying to build an algorithm that
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,deals with
