Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how do you deal with the racial bias
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the long list of questions we should think about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when developing and deploying technology
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:54.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so let's start by answering this question
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.47,0:10:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so here's what we did
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we want to enter a crowd sourcing website
