Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you pay people a couple of bucks
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.50,0:11:03.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and they answer a bunch of questions for you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.67,0:11:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and you can collect
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.53,0:11:06.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,thousands and thousands of these data
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.17,0:11:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,within a matter of days
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and get a sense of how do people make these judgments
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.87,0:11:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now obviously these are not judges lawyers
