Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.70,0:11:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so surely this will be a lower bar for performance
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.20,0:11:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but we wanted to start there
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then we'll see where we are
