Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.40,0:27:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so now what I'm going to do is I'm going to find a line
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.80,0:27:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,such that when I project
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.40,0:27:30.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all the data onto that one dimensional subspace
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.13,0:27:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to accomplish two things
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.13,0:27:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the first thing is I'm going to minimize
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.67,0:27:39.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the within class variants
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.90,0:27:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so classes red did recidivate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.77,0:27:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or yellow did not recidivate
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.07,0:27:46.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and what I want is
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.17,0:27:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to find a line that as I rotate through this
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.17,0:27:52.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,space all of the red dots are bundled up really
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.73,0:27:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,really tightly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.93,0:27:54.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and all of the
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.97,0:27:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,yellow dots are bundled up really tightly
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.87,0:28:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that's the within class red yellow variance
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.40,0:28:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to minimize those variances so that
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.50,0:28:05.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all everybody's
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.90,0:28:07.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,tightly bungled up together
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.00,0:28:11.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and at the same time I want to maximize
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.33,0:28:13.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the across class variants
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.47,0:28:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that is I want
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.80,0:28:17.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,these red dots to be really tightly coupled
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.10,0:28:18.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and to be very far away
