Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.20,0:28:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,different objective functions
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.97,0:28:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not necessarily good or bad
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.53,0:28:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that this is probably the simplest one
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.50,0:28:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you will learn this in your machine learning class
