Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.07,0:28:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,when
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.60,0:28:59.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you specify the problem is minimizing within class
