Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.53,0:29:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,natural language processing
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.77,0:29:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the long list of really cool things out there
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.13,0:29:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you need to know a lot of math
