Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.90,0:29:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,code really nice really simple very efficient
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.37,0:29:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now once I have that classifier
