Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.20,0:41:35.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,understanding of now of the space
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.00,0:41:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and now the question is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.17,0:41:38.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,can you get rid of bias
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.60,0:41:40.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and can you make the accuracies better
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.87,0:41:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,okay so let me just talk very briefly
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.40,0:41:44.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,about some of the work we've done on that
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.13,0:41:45.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so the first thing we asked is
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.57,0:41:48.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,well what happens if we go from a linear classifier
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.13,0:41:49.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the simplest possible classifier
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.87,0:41:51.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you can build to a
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.80,0:41:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,non linear classifier
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.20,0:41:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and without going into the details of it
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.07,0:41:58.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a non linear classifier basically allows you to build
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.20,0:42:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,not just a line through this space but a curvy
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.37,0:42:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,a curve that allows you to carve out exceptions
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.17,0:42:07.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,right so here you can see for example
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.20,0:42:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm carving around here so I have
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.33,0:42:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,more of the yellow points down below
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.00,0:42:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and more of the red points above
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.60,0:42:14.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so these are called nonlinear classifiers
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.67,0:42:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,support bacter machines neural networks deep learning
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.00,0:42:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all of those fall
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.07,0:42:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,into that category of nonlinear classifier
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.90,0:42:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and just one nonlinear classifier that we build
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.53,0:42:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,was really really disappointing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.93,0:42:26.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,again this is the overall
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.93,0:42:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,accuracy of the commercial software 65%
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.33,0:42:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,our human 64%
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.97,0:42:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the linear classifier
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.93,0:42:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the lda that we've already talked about was 66%
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.93,0:42:38.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the non linear was 65%
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.27,0:42:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,they're all exactly the same
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.87,0:42:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we just seem to be stuck at around 65 %
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.07,0:42:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,okay I posit I cannot prove but I posit
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.73,0:42:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I think that this is a fundamentally hard problem
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.30,0:42:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I am unconvinced
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.07,0:42:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that you can actually do better than this
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.50,0:42:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because think about what you're asking
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.47,0:42:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the algorithm to do
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.07,0:42:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you're asking it to predict the future
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.10,0:43:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,from a relatively small amount of data
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.53,0:43:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the future two years in advance
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.13,0:43:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of a fairly complex set of socioeconomic personal
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.93,0:43:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and just what is
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.97,0:43:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,random dumb luck going to happen in somebody's life
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.50,0:43:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I don't think that's a stretch of imagination
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.40,0:43:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,to say that this is really hard
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.80,0:43:20.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so here's a question for you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.53,0:43:22.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,should we even be doing this
Dialogue: 0,0:43:22.47,0:43:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,should we actually be trying to predict
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.80,0:43:25.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,whether
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.13,0:43:27.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,somebody's going to commit a crime in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.37,0:43:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and then incarcerate them if we think that they are
Dialogue: 0,0:43:30.50,0:43:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if the actor is 65%
Dialogue: 0,0:43:33.17,0:43:36.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what if the accuracy 75% what if it's 85%
Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.50,0:43:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what if it's you
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.60,0:43:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what if it's somebody you love
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.77,0:43:41.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do you want this algorithm being applied to somebody
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.30,0:43:42.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with this kind of error rate
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.40,0:43:43.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what's an acceptable error rate
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.77,0:43:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are these things really better than humans
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.37,0:43:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,how do you deal with the bias
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.47,0:43:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,nobody has good answers to these things
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.70,0:43:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,so here's a question
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.33,0:43:54.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,now I come back to the title right
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.67,0:43:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,just because you can do something
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.87,0:43:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,doesn't mean you should
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.00,0:44:01.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and as you enter into
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.40,0:44:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what is undoubtedly an incredibly exciting
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.30,0:44:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,time for us in terms of
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.20,0:44:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,computation and ai and data
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.90,0:44:10.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the impact that we can have on the world
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.87,0:44:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have to start thinking about
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.20,0:44:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,what are the negative aspects of what we are doing
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.40,0:44:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,should we be trying to make these decisions
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.40,0:44:20.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and if we do the answer may be yes
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.93,0:44:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but then are they accurate
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.07,0:44:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,are they fair
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.27,0:44:26.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,do they disproportionately affect women
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.27,0:44:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,people of color lgbtq community
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.13,0:44:30.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,people who are not born in this country
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.77,0:44:32.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,people who aren't native speakers
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.13,0:44:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.70,0:44:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have to think about the consequences of that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.37,0:44:37.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have spent the last 20
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.80,0:44:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,years with the mantra of move fast and break things
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.67,0:44:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and while lots of good things have come from that
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.70,0:44:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,some really bad things have come from this
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.17,0:44:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bias and algorithms for hiring
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.90,0:44:49.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bias and algorims and healthcare
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.37,0:44:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bias for algorithms in financial sectors
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.47,0:44:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bias for algorims in the criminal justice system
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.77,0:44:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,bias in facial recognition
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.70,0:44:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we've got to tread lightly here
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.17,0:45:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and what that means is you can't come at this
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.37,0:45:03.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,after the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.10,0:45:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,you can't develop deploy and then debug on the fly
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.53,0:45:10.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this isn't a word processing software
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.33,0:45:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,if you have a bug somebody loses a document
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.40,0:45:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this is the real world where you make a mistake
Dialogue: 0,0:45:15.90,0:45:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in somebody sitting in jail
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.30,0:45:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or somebody doesn't get a home loan
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.77,0:45:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or somebody doesn't get a small business loan
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.70,0:45:23.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or somebody doesn't get a job or go to the university
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.40,0:45:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we are impacting real people's lives
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.80,0:45:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,with our algorithms and our data
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.70,0:45:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and if we don't understand these things
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.07,0:45:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we have the potential to do way more harm
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.10,0:45:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,than we do good
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.47,0:45:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and so the free for all of the last two decades
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.87,0:45:38.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,in my opinion
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.97,0:45:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,should be over
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.00,0:45:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I want to emphasize that I am not anti technology
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.60,0:45:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying don't do things
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.87,0:45:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not saying don't innovate
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.33,0:45:47.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm saying think
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.10,0:45:49.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,think carefully about
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.67,0:45:51.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,the consequences of what you are doing
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.37,0:45:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and make sure that there is transparency
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.60,0:45:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,there is fairness and there is accuracy
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.93,0:45:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and how these technologies are being used
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.70,0:45:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and more generally
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.10,0:46:00.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,making sure that you
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.13,0:46:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,understand how your technologies can be
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.73,0:46:03.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,misused as well
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.40,0:46:03.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,because
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.77,0:46:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,almost all technologies have benefits and drawbacks
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.47,0:46:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we have to start
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.40,0:46:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,thinking about those things up front
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.27,0:46:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and simply try to mitigate the harm
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.27,0:46:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,while harnessing the phenomenal power
Dialogue: 0,0:46:13.77,0:46:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,of technology and ai and data
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.73,0:46:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,all right I'm done
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.53,0:46:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you enjoyed this
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.30,0:46:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and I hope you learned something from it
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.47,0:46:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and we'll see you soon